2001 Acura Integra Clean titled vehicle offered here at Horizon Auto Group, Inc. Take a look at this beautiful Integra coming in a sharp Taffeta White color. It features a sun / moon roof, automatic transmission, ice cold A/C, spare tire, cruise control, tinted windows, hatch trunk, and more. This vehicle is ready to go and be owned today. It has a clean interior and exterior. You will get good gas MPG with this Integra, getting 21 in the city and 28 on the highway. The timeless styling and sporty coupe silhouette make this vehicle beautiful for many years come. Be sure to come by and experience this Acura Integra for yourself today. Come now before it's gone. This is the one for you! If you have any questions, inquries or would like to test drive, contact: HORIZON AUTO GROUP 6780 Narcoossee Rd Orlando, FL 32822 (321) 281-9443 Office (407) 580-5785 Danny (407) 747-4245 Efrain Hablamos español
